		"inclusion": "1) Put Z-Wave controller into Add mode. See Z-Wave controller documentation for further information.\n2) Press the NETWORKING button on the side of the control unit. The Z-Wave LED will begin to blink. \n3) The valve has been successfully added to the network when the Z-Wave LED becomes solid.",
